    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一家人聚在一起温馨庆祝，但每个人看起来都很沮丧！这是怎么回事？这些人（还有宠物）是谁？！他们为什么这么不开心？！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279410/extras/f3f9fd9356d68083d1039905cb2f4a10.avif?t=1766008032\" width=1560 height=188 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从家里的狗到脾气暴躁的奶奶，窥探他们不幸的生活，调查导致聚会发生的事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279410/extras/0bfc81e7a23a1af4894d96b445bc6163.poster.avif?t=1766008032\" width=800 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279410/extras/0bfc81e7a23a1af4894d96b445bc6163.webm?t=1766008032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279410/extras/0bfc81e7a23a1af4894d96b445bc6163.mp4?t=1766008032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279410/extras/367a227f187da895d6c6d664784625b2.avif?t=1766008032\" width=1560 height=188 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仔细查看每一幅手绘场景，寻找指向人物身份、动机和遭遇的线索。认真阅读，彻底搜寻，准备好接受你的推理能力考验吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279410/extras/e91cf55f3ffbe724c65b33c43d076be1.poster.avif?t=1766008032\" width=1050 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279410/extras/e91cf55f3ffbe724c65b33c43d076be1.webm?t=1766008032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279410/extras/e91cf55f3ffbe724c65b33c43d076be1.mp4?t=1766008032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279410/extras/673c69b5a54b02c1a7e2e924a0dee4e9.avif?t=1766008032\" width=1560 height=188 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从这10个充满惊喜、背叛和混乱的棘手案件中得出你自己的结论！你有能力破案吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特点</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>难度递增</strong>——从轻松简单到真正烧脑，准备好磨练你的侦探技能吧！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>提示系统</strong>——遇到难题？使用游戏内置的提示系统，轻松找到线索。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>填空式结论</strong>——利用每个案件中收集到的词语，得出你自己的结论。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏内记事本</strong>——使用游戏内记事本记录重要线索。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>轻松愉快的案件</strong>——享受轻松幽默、贴近生活的推理故事，没有阴暗的主题。</p></li></ul>",
